'''Syrio Forel''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 1|first season]]. He is played by guest star [[Miltos Yerolemou]] and debuts in &quot;[[Lord Snow]].&quot; Syrio Forel is a master sword-fighter and instructor hired by [[Eddard Stark]] to train [[Arya Stark]].

